{
  "id": "5d79be488c3ae60017aad3b9",
  "title": "リスクと脆弱性",
  "created": 1568259659,
  "updated": 1676300574,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5d79be488c3ae60017aad3b9",
      "text": "リスクと脆弱性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259659,
      "updated": 1568259663
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0adc6aff09e0000ca87b3",
      "text": "反脆弱性勉強会",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643163078,
      "updated": 1643163085
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be50aff09e0000e26f51",
      "text": "　書籍[反脆弱性]が話題になった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259665,
      "updated": 1643163103
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0ae0daff09e0000ca87b5",
      "text": "　「反脆弱性の定義は？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643163149,
      "updated": 1643163157
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0add5aff09e0000ca87b4",
      "text": "　議論の前提になる知識を整理する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643163093,
      "updated": 1643163107
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be62aff09e0000e26f52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259683,
      "updated": 1568259683
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be4eaff09e0000e26f47",
      "text": "\t[リスク]の大きさをどう定量化するか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259663,
      "updated": 1643162804
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be4faff09e0000e26f48",
      "text": "\t\t[標準偏差]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259663,
      "updated": 1643162788
    },
    {
      "id": "5d7b17f3aff09e0000d3074a",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ \\sqrt{\\mathbb{E}[(X-\\mu)^2]} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568348148,
      "updated": 1568348254
    },
    {
      "id": "5d7b180faff09e0000d3074b",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ \\sqrt{\\sum (x - \\mu)^2 P(X=x)} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568348175,
      "updated": 1568348261
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be4faff09e0000e26f49",
      "text": "\t\t 変化しない ゼロ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259663,
      "updated": 1568259663
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be4faff09e0000e26f4a",
      "text": "\t\t 1万が、0万か2万か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259663,
      "updated": 1568259663
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be4faff09e0000e26f4b",
      "text": "\t\t  標準偏差 1万円",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259663,
      "updated": 1568259663
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be4faff09e0000e26f4c",
      "text": "\t\t 宝くじ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259663,
      "updated": 1568259663
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c204aff09e00006f2b0d",
      "text": "\t\t \t例: 1/2000万の確率で7億円",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568260612,
      "updated": 1568260644
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c245aff09e00006f2b0e",
      "text": "\t\t \t\t計算が面倒なので他の細々した賞は無視する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568260677,
      "updated": 1568260695
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c256aff09e00006f2b0f",
      "text": "\t\t \t\t期待値35円",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568260695,
      "updated": 1568260701
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c297aff09e00006f2b10",
      "text": "\t\t \t\t1/2000万の確率で7億-35円プラス、残りの確率で-265円",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568260759,
      "updated": 1568260785
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c2b1aff09e00006f2b11",
      "text": "\t\t \t\tsqrt(2.45e9 + 70225)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568260785,
      "updated": 1568260974
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c369aff09e0000e26f53",
      "text": "\t\t \t\t標準偏差は5万円ぐらい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568260969,
      "updated": 1568261017
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c3c9aff09e0000e26f56",
      "text": "\t\t \t\t\t5万が0万か10万かになる賭けと同じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568261065,
      "updated": 1568261081
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79be4faff09e0000e26f4d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t  一般的には期待値150円、標準偏差16万円くらいになるらしい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568259663,
      "updated": 1568261086
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c3ecaff09e0000e26f57",
      "text": "\t\t\t逆宝くじ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568261100,
      "updated": 1568265119
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d39faff09e00006f2b39",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t300円もらえるけど、1/2000万の確率で7億円取られる博打",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265119,
      "updated": 1568265135
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d3aeaff09e00006f2b3a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこれももちろんリスクの程度は同じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265135,
      "updated": 1568265145
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c383aff09e0000e26f54",
      "text": "\t\t[ダウンサイドリスク]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568260995,
      "updated": 1643162707
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c453aff09e00006f2b12",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\sqrt { \\mathbb{E}[(X-\\mu)^{2}]1_{\\{X\\leq\\mu\\}} } ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568261204,
      "updated": 1568348366
    },
    {
      "id": "5d7b188caff09e0000d3074c",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\sqrt{\\sum (X - \\mu) ^2 1_{\\{X\\leq\\mu\\}}} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568348300,
      "updated": 1568348367
    },
    {
      "id": "5d7b18cbaff09e0000d3074d",
      "text": "\t\t\t誤: [$ \\mathbb{E}_{\\{X\\leq\\mu\\}}[(X-\\mu)^{2}] ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568348363,
      "updated": 1568348406
    },
    {
      "id": "5d7b18faaff09e0000d3074e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t勘違いしていた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568348410,
      "updated": 1568348415
    },
    {
      "id": "5d7b1915aff09e0000d30750",
      "text": "\t\t\t一般に[$ \\mu ]だけではなく、注目する点kを定めた時のダウンサイドリスクを議論したりする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568348438,
      "updated": 1568348473
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c4e6aff09e00006f2b14",
      "text": "\t\t 宝くじのダウンサイドリスクは...",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568261350,
      "updated": 1568348418
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79c423aff09e0000e26f58",
      "text": "\t\t 5万が0万か10万かになる賭けのダウンサイドリスクは...",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568261156,
      "updated": 1568348421
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d3bcaff09e00006f2b3b",
      "text": "\t\t 逆宝くじのダウンサイドリスクは...",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265148,
      "updated": 1568348422
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79f97daff09e0000fbbf90",
      "text": "\t\t\t下に行くほど大きくなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568274813,
      "updated": 1568348427
    },
    {
      "id": "63ea510baff09e00007f6620",
      "text": "\t\t\t対義語: [アップサイドリスク]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676300556,
      "updated": 1676300574
    },
    {
      "id": "5d7b190baff09e0000d3074f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568348427,
      "updated": 1568348427
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cd2aaff09e0000e26f59",
      "text": "\tbetaの概念",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263466,
      "updated": 1568263470
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cd2daff09e0000e26f5b",
      "text": "\t\tある確率変数Xと確率変数Y",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263470,
      "updated": 1568263483
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cd3daff09e0000e26f5c",
      "text": "\t\t[$ Y = \\alpha + \\beta X + \\epsilon ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263486,
      "updated": 1568263506
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cd86aff09e0000e26f5e",
      "text": "\t\tこの時",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263559,
      "updated": 1568263561
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cd2baff09e0000e26f5a",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\beta = \\frac{Cov(X, Y)}{Var(Y)} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263468,
      "updated": 1568263548
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d2d5aff09e00006f2b34",
      "text": "\tベースアセットXが株式だとする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264917,
      "updated": 1568264932
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d2e3aff09e00006f2b35",
      "text": "\t\t借金して10倍の量の株式を買うとbetaは約10倍になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264932,
      "updated": 1568264963
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d3ddaff09e00006f2b3c",
      "text": "\t\t\tいわゆる「[レバレッジ]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265182,
      "updated": 1643162722
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d306aff09e00006f2b36",
      "text": "\t\tその計算で本当に良いのか？と疑問視されるようになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264967,
      "updated": 1568265075
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d373aff09e00006f2b37",
      "text": "\t\t[ロングターム・キャピタル・マネジメント - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0%E3%82%BF%E3%83%BC%E3%83%A0%E3%83%BB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A3%E3%83%94%E3%82%BF%E3%83%AB%E3%83%BB%E3%83%9E%E3%83%8D%E3%82%B8%E3%83%A1%E3%83%B3%E3%83%88]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265075,
      "updated": 1568265076
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d374aff09e00006f2b38",
      "text": "\t\t\t高い運用成績を出していたが、それはレバレッジによるもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265077,
      "updated": 1568265180
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cd65aff09e0000e26f5d",
      "text": "\tこのVarianceに関してもdownsideについて考えた方が良いのではないかという議論が行われるようになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263525,
      "updated": 1643162759
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cd96aff09e0000e26f5f",
      "text": "\t\t→downside betaの概念の登場",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263574,
      "updated": 1643162768
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d2d3aff09e00006f2b33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264915,
      "updated": 1568264915
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cdd3aff09e0000e26f62",
      "text": "\tvolatilityの概念",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263635,
      "updated": 1568263641
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cdd9aff09e0000e26f64",
      "text": "\t\ttime horizonを固定した上での標準偏差",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263641,
      "updated": 1568263713
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0ad0baff09e0000ca87b2",
      "text": "\t\t宝くじのリスクの話で「当選番号発表後」の標準偏差を考えた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643162891,
      "updated": 1643162950
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79ce31aff09e00006f2b16",
      "text": "\t\t文脈としてオプション価格の変動が想定されてることが多い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263730,
      "updated": 1568263765
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79ce55aff09e00006f2b17",
      "text": "\t\t\t日々連続的に価格変動するので「一定の日数後の価格の分布」を考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263765,
      "updated": 1568263788
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79ce6caff09e00006f2b18",
      "text": "\t\tしばしば [$ \\sigma ]と書く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263788,
      "updated": 1568263806
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cde4aff09e0000e26f65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263653,
      "updated": 1568263653
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cdeaaff09e0000e26f66",
      "text": "\tvegaの概念",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263659,
      "updated": 1568263661
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cdedaff09e0000e26f67",
      "text": "\t[$ \\frac{\\partial V}{\\partial \\sigma}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263661,
      "updated": 1568263829
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cdd5aff09e0000e26f63",
      "text": "\t\tオプション価格をvolatilityで微分したもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263639,
      "updated": 1568263844
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cea4aff09e00006f2b1b",
      "text": "\t\t例えば「1ヶ月後の価格が今の価格のプラマイ10%に収まっていれば1万円あげるけど、収まってなければ1万円取る」というオプション取引を考えた時に、ベースになるアセットのvolatilityが高いほどこのオプションの価格は下がる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263844,
      "updated": 1568263982
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cf2eaff09e00006f2b1c",
      "text": "\t\t\t→負のvega",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263982,
      "updated": 1568263998
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cf3aaff09e00006f2b1d",
      "text": "\t\tストックオプション",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263994,
      "updated": 1568264019
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cf52aff09e00006f2b1e",
      "text": "\t\t\t「将来X株得る権利」を今の現金給与100万円と交換するオプション",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264019,
      "updated": 1568264057
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cf79aff09e00006f2b1f",
      "text": "\t\t\t株が紙くずになると-100万円",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264057,
      "updated": 1568264072
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cf87aff09e00006f2b20",
      "text": "\t\t\tX株の株価が200万になると+100万",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264072,
      "updated": 1568264089
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cf98aff09e00006f2b21",
      "text": "\t\t\tvolatilityが高いほど期待値も上がる(0以下にならないため)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264089,
      "updated": 1568264315
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d07caff09e00006f2b2a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tストックオプションの価値は高まる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264317,
      "updated": 1568264318
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cfc2aff09e00006f2b22",
      "text": "\t\t\t→正のvega",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264130,
      "updated": 1568264143
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cfcfaff09e00006f2b23",
      "text": "\t\tサイボウズの持株会",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264144,
      "updated": 1568264157
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cfddaff09e00006f2b24",
      "text": "\t\t\t現時点での現金X円と引き換えに現時点での2X円分の株を得るオプション",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264157,
      "updated": 1568264186
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79cff6aff09e00006f2b26",
      "text": "\t\t\t株価が変動しなければ+X円",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264183,
      "updated": 1568264197
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d004aff09e00006f2b27",
      "text": "\t\t\t株価が上がればまあ嬉しい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264197,
      "updated": 1568264202
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d00aaff09e00006f2b28",
      "text": "\t\t\t株価が半額以下に下がると損",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264202,
      "updated": 1568264208
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d011aff09e00006f2b29",
      "text": "\t\t\t現時点価格から0円になる確率を無視すると期待値は変わらない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264209,
      "updated": 1568264396
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d0cbaff09e00006f2b2b",
      "text": "\t\t\tオプション価格は？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264396,
      "updated": 1568264399
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d0cfaff09e00006f2b2c",
      "text": "\t\t\tvolatilityが高いほど[リスクプレミアム]分だけ下がる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264399,
      "updated": 1643163143
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79ce9baff09e00006f2b1a",
      "text": "\t\t\t→負のvega",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568263836,
      "updated": 1568264419
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d0e3aff09e00006f2b2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264419,
      "updated": 1568264419
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d125aff09e00006f2b2e",
      "text": "\t脆弱性(fragility)とは何か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264485,
      "updated": 1568264496
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d127aff09e00006f2b2f",
      "text": "\t\tleft-side vegaである",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264488,
      "updated": 1643163194
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d171aff09e00006f2b31",
      "text": "\t\tつまり「リスク→ダウンサイドリスク」、「beta→downside beta」と同じ構図をvegaに対して使ったもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264562,
      "updated": 1643163205
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d42aaff09e00006f2b3e",
      "text": "\t\t逆宝くじの例",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265258,
      "updated": 1568265275
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d43baff09e00006f2b3f",
      "text": "\t\t\tdownsideでないリスクは「だいたい得をするがごく稀に大損が発生する」と「だいたい損をするがごく稀に大儲けする」を区別できなかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265276,
      "updated": 1660661328
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d478aff09e00006f2b40",
      "text": "\t\t同様にdownsideでないvegaはごく稀に発生する「volatilityがとても高い状態」(ベースアセットの暴騰・暴落 )をうまく扱えない？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265336,
      "updated": 1568265507
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d523aff09e00006f2b41",
      "text": "\t\tleft-sideとはX軸に対象の値をとって確率分布を描いた場合ダウンサイドが左であることを指す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265507,
      "updated": 1643163349
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d529aff09e00006f2b42",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265513,
      "updated": 1568265513
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d183aff09e00006f2b32",
      "text": "\trobustとは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568264579,
      "updated": 1568265235
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d413aff09e00006f2b3d",
      "text": "\t\tfragilityが少ないこと？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265235,
      "updated": 1568265542
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0aeddaff09e0000ca87b6",
      "text": "\t\t分布形状の安定性の話をしている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643163358,
      "updated": 1643163377
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d533aff09e00006f2b43",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265524,
      "updated": 1568265524
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d534aff09e00006f2b44",
      "text": "\tantifragilityとは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265524,
      "updated": 1568265539
    },
    {
      "id": "5d7b16f6aff09e0000d30749",
      "text": "\t\t>Antifragility is not the simple opposite of fragility, as we saw in Table 1. Measuring antifragility, on the one hand, consists of the flipside of fragility on the right-hand side, but on the other hand requires a control on the robustness of the probability distribution on the left-hand side. From that aspect, unlike fragility, antifragility cannot be summarized in one single figure but necessitates at least two of them.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568347894,
      "updated": 1568347909
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d537aff09e00006f2b45",
      "text": "\t\tFragility(downside vega)を右側に折り返したものと、Robustnessを組み合わせた概念",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265528,
      "updated": 1643163385
    },
    {
      "id": "5d79d5fbaff09e00006f2b47",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1568265723,
      "updated": 1568265723
    }
  ]
}